  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>bulgur</strong> to a pot with plenty of boiled water (the same as you would for pasta) and cook over a high heat for 10-15 min or until tender with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>halloumi</strong> in half lengthways (where the natural crease forms)</p>\r\n<p>Add 500ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml]&nbsp;</span>boiled water to&nbsp;a pot and return to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, carefully add the halloumi slices and boil for 5-8 min or until they've softened&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut&nbsp;the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;in half</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>chilli jam</strong> with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir until the jam has dissolved</p>\r\n<p>Add the juice of half the<strong> lemon</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> - this is your sweet chilli dressing</p>\r\n<p>Top and tail and cut the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;into bite-size pieces&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, drain and pat the <strong>halloumi</strong> slices dry with a clean tea towel or kitchen paper</p>\r\n<p>Using&nbsp;a rolling pin, flatten and roll out each piece until they are a little larger than a post-it note&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>courgette</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-6 min or until golden&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once golden, transfer the courgette to a small plate and keep the pan for step 7</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel&nbsp;the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot 'ribbons'</p>\r\n<p>Chop<strong>&nbsp;</strong>the <strong>pea shoots</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat and once hot, add the <strong>halloumi</strong> slices &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cook each side for 1-2 min or until golden</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>bulgur wheat</strong>, <strong>carrot ribbons</strong>, <strong>pea shoots</strong> and <strong>courgette</strong> in a large salad bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a squeeze of <strong>lemon</strong> and mix to combine&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/715.-step--7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the golden halloumi over the salad and drizzle the chilli lemon dressing over&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Garnish with the remaining lemon, cut into wedges</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
